---
// Projects 목록 — 2열 카드 그리드 (커버·프로젝트명·태그라인·스택 칩)
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';

const projects = (await getCollection('projects')).sort((a, b) =>
  b.data.created.localeCompare(a.data.created),
);
---

<Base title="Projects · angari.dev" description="프로젝트 쇼케이스" current="projects">
  <div class="list-head">
    <h1 class="page-title">Projects</h1>
    <p class="page-desc">만든 것들. 제작기는 시리즈로 이어집니다.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="project-grid">
    {
      projects.map((p) => (
        <a class="project-card" href={`/projects/${p.id}`}>
          <Image class="cover" src={p.data.cover} alt={`${p.data.title} 스크린샷`} />
          <span class="card-body">
            <span class="card-title">{p.data.title}</span>
            <span class="card-tagline">{p.data.tagline}</span>
            <span class="stack-chips">
              {p.data.stacks.map((stack) => (
                <span class="chip">{stack}</span>
              ))}
            </span>
          </span>
        </a>
      ))
    }
  </div>
  {projects.length === 0 && <p class="page-desc">등록된 프로젝트가 아직 없다.</p>}
</Base>

<style>
  .list-head {
    padding: 16px 0 10px;
  }
  .project-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .project-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
  .project-card {
    display: block;
    border: 1px solid var(--c-bd);
    border-radius: 14px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--c-bg2);
  }
  .project-card :global(.cover) {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 88px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .card-body {
    display: block;
    padding: 13px 14px 15px;
  }
  .card-title {
    display: block;
    font: 700 15px/1.2 var(--font-sans);
    color: var(--c-tx);
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }
  .card-tagline {
    display: block;
    font: 500 12px/1.5 var(--font-sans);
    color: var(--c-tx2);
    margin-bottom: 11px;
    min-height: 2.4em;
  }
  .stack-chips {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .chip {
    font: 600 10px/1 var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--c-tx3);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-bd);
    border-radius: 5px;
    padding: 4px 7px;
  }
</style>
